headline: CSX Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer to Address Baird Global Industrial Conference
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., Nov. 04, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- CSX Corp. (NASDAQ: CSX) Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer, Kevin Boone, will address the 2025 Baird Global Industrial Conference in Chicago on Tuesday, November 11, at 10:05 a.m. Eastern time. This address will be broadcast live via webcast at http://investors.csx.com. A replay will be available following the conclusion of this event. headline: 1 Nasdaq 100 Stock on Our Watchlist and 2 We Avoid
summary: The Nasdaq 100 (^NDX) is home to some of the biggest success stories in tech and growth investing. However, certain stocks in the index face challenges like profitability concerns, rising costs, or shifts in market trends.
